				<h2 class="bottomSpace">About Us</h2>
				
				<h3 class="bottomSpace">About Next2Friends</h3>
				<p>
	
					Next2Friends, the mobile social media platform, was created to deliver content and 
					connections that entertain, engage and enhance life. Bringing together the full 
					capabilities of both mobile and PC-based internet technology, the comprehensive 
					suite of applications and features provide rich media, commercial and communication 
					services to today’s connected consumer.
				</p>
				<p>
					The Next2Friends platform utilises patent-pending, proprietary technology to ensure 
					consumers, businesses and brands enjoy the full value of the mobile internet. The 
					UK Limited Company, formed in 2007, has offices in the UK and US, in addition to 
					R&amp;D divisions on three continents.
				</p>
				
				<h3 class="bottomSpace">What This Means...</h3>
				
				<p>
					Next2Friends is on a mission to help you get the best out of life! We all carry 
					mobile phones with us everywhere we go, but often only use them for boring 
					things like making phone calls! Next2Friends opens up a whole new world of fun and 
					interaction using the kit you carry round in your pocket.
				</p>
				
				<h3 class="bottomSpace">Get more out of your mobile...</h3>
				
				<p>
					Next2Friends’ mobile apps understand how you want to use your phone and how you 
					want to live your life. They help people share life as it happens, in all its glory; 
					get feedback and make decisions; and connect with people who have similar interests. 
				</p>
				
				<p>
					What you can do with your phone &amp; Next2Friends:
				</p>
				
				<ul class="bulleted">
					<li>
						<strong>Live</strong> – stream real-time videos from your phone to the 
						web that are viewable by everyone or just the select few.
					</li>
					<li>
						<strong>Ask</strong> – get advice and opinions from people who count about 
						things you want to buy or do.
					</li>
					<li>
						<strong>Snap Up</strong> – instantly share photos and images without filling 
						up your phone or paying expensive MMS charges.
					</li>
					<li>
						<strong>Tag &amp; Meet</strong> – find and make friends with people like you... and nearby too!
					</li>
				</ul>
				
				<h3 class="bottomSpace">Do more online...</h3>
				
				<p>
					www.Next2Friends.com offers even more for you to do. From either your mobile browser 
					or your computer, explore the latest, greatest videos from other members, find and 
					network with people from all over the world and get the latest developments and new features.
				</p>
				
				<h3>Staying in touch:</h3>
				
				<ul class="bulleted">
					<li>
						<strong>Chat</strong> – on the page you’re looking at or in a new window.
					</li>
					<li>
						<strong>Video Messaging</strong> – one to one or one to many! However you want to keep people in the know.
					</li>
					<li>
						<strong>Blogging</strong> – update your friends in seconds, then embed it on other sites 
						for more people to enjoy. You can even bring blogs from elsewhere onto your 
						Next2Friends profile.
					</li>
					<li>
						<strong>Email</strong> – standard stuff these days, but of course we do that for you too! 
					</li>
				</ul>
				
				<h3>Socialising:</h3>
				
				<ul class="bulleted">
					<li>
						<strong>Profiles</strong> – create a rich and personal introduction to you, your 
						life and the world you live in.
					</li>
					<li>
						<strong>Networking</strong> – invite friends both online and in the real world to 
						join you on Next2Friends. 
					</li>
					<li>
						<strong>Communities</strong> – find and get involved with brands, bands and artists you like. 
					</li>
					<li>
						<strong>Updates</strong> – newsfeeds, favourites, homepage showcases and alerts... 
						lots of ways to keep up with everything of interest on Next2Friends.
					</li>
					<li>
						<strong>Sharing</strong> – grab the content you like and add it to other blogs and 
						social networks in seconds.
					</li>
				</ul>
				
