				<h3 class="bottomSpace">Simon Property Group INC (NYSE: SPG)</h3>
				
				<p>
					Next2Friends has formed a strategic relationship with Simon Property Group 
					Inc., an S&P 500 company and the largest public U.S. real estate company. 
					Simon is a fully integrated real estate company which operates from five 
					retail real estate platforms: regional malls, Premium Outlet Centers&reg;, 
					The Mills&reg;, community/lifestyle centers and international properties. It 
					currently owns or has an interest in 382 properties comprising 260 million 
