				<h3 class="bottomSpace">DropJaw Ventures Limited</h3>
				
				<p>
					Next2Friends is part funded by DropJaw Ventures Limited, an early stage Investor 
					into emerging and aspiring technology companies. DropJaw typically looks for young 
					organisations which have disruptive technology, a high growth potential and with 
					a management team with zest, enthusiasm and that rare commitment to succeed. DropJaw 
					Ventures can lead, but typically invests alongside the management team and or other 
					early stage Angel Investors and Venture Capitalists. 
				</p>
				
				<p>
					Not only can DropJaw Ventures provide that all important early stage seed and A 
					round capital, it can also provide a range of value added services which will 
					deliver tangible returns for all stakeholders.
				</p>
				
				<p>
					For further information: <a href="http://www.dropjawventures.co.uk">www.dropjawventures.co.uk</a>
				</p>
				
				<h3 class="bottomSpace">Genetibase Inc.</h3>
				
				<p>
					Next2Friends was the original concept spinning out of Genetibase, which still 
					takes the lead role in all research and development of the Next2Friends platform.
				</p>
				
				<p>
					Genetibase, Inc focus is software for Scientific Markets including but not limited to: 
					Biology (Medicine: Human, Veterinary and Dental), Chemistry, Physics, Mathematics, 
					Software Developer Tools and Components in which applications can vary widely in 
					application. Our platform focus is primarily Microsoft.Net Technologies upon 
					Windows Operating Systems.
				</p>
				
				<p>
					Our applications and software development services range from Insurance Industries, 
					Manufacturing, Data Modeling, Medical and Information Analysis Industries. As well 
					we offer IT/IS consultation services and custom programming services to additional 
					industries and or markets on a project by project basis.
				</p>
				
				<p>
					For further information: <a href="http://www.genetibase.com">www.genetibase.com</a>
				</p>
				
				<h3 class="bottomSpace">Pussycat Club</h3>
				
				<p>
					The Pussycat Club is one of the longest running, most highly respected club brands 
					in the UK. Next2Friends is working with the team to show people at their parties 
					how to get more out of their mobiles as well as stream the fun and festivities live 
					onto Next2Friends for everyone around the world to enjoy. With a range of performance 
					artists, competitions, activities and costumed hostesses, as well as top flight, 
					cutting edge DJs, Pussycat promoters create a visually rich, glamorous and theatrical 
					extravaganza of an event.
				</p>
				
				<p>
					The Pussycat Club has built up a fantastically loyal following over the last 13 years 
